Rebrand Code OSS to Code Editor (TypeScript support)

Adds codeEditorVersion to the product type definitions and customizes
the About dialog to show Code Editor version alongside Code-OSS version.

Note: product.json changes are in product-config.diff (generated patch).
In 1.111.x, the dialog.ts file moved from src/vs/platform/dialogs/browser/
to src/vs/workbench/browser/parts/dialogs/.

